MoneyMotivationalMoreComputerMobileFestivalHMHHomeBloggingQuora se Website ki Quality Traffic kaise BadhayeBloggingQuora se Website ki Quality Traffic kaise BadhayeBy Rohit Mewada - October 30, 201742Facebook Twitter Google+ WhatsApp PinterestWebsite Traffic kaise badaye aksar har blogger ke man me yaha sawal rahta ki waha napne blog par traffic kaise badaye to chaliye aaj ham apko ek esa tarika batane wale hai jisse aap apne blog par 35% tak or jyada traffic bada lenge.Apne blog ya site par aap traffic lane ke liye kai tarike aajmaye honge jaise Social Media Shareor On Page SEO, Off Page SEO or bhi bahut se tarike har blogger aajmata hai.lekin me jo apko tarika batane wala hu yaha Off page seo ka ek part hai jisse aap apne blog par quaility traffic bada sakenge, isi trick se mene apne blog par 40% or jyada traffic badaya hai ro me apko bata du me bat kar raha hu Quora ki.Quora Kya hai ?Quora ek esi website hai jaha aap apne kisi bhi sawal ka jawab puch sakte hai or agar aap ko kisi sawal ke bare me achhe se pata hai to aap uska jawab de sakte hai.Quora kafi popular site hai yaha aap apne knowledge ko bada sakte hai or apne knowledge ko dunia tak pahucha sakte hai.Quora se Website ke traffic ko kaise badaye ?To ab ham aate hai apne topic par ki ham kis tarah Quora se apne blog par traffic ko bada sakte hai to chaliye ham batate hai apko iske bare me puri jankari hindi me.Sabse pahle apko Quora.com par apna account banana hai, jo aap aasani se Login with Facebook karke bana sakte hai.Jaise ki apko pata hai Quora ek question and answer site hai jaha apko apne har sawal ka jawab asani se mil jayega to apko karna kya hai apni website se related topic ke upar ke sawalo ke jawab dena hai or usme apko apne blog ki link paste karne hai.Sawalo ke jawab kaise de ?jaise hi aap apne Quora account se login karenge apke samne ek window open hogi jaise ki is image me diya hai.Ab apke samne kuch sawal dikhenge apko jis bhi sawal ke bare me achhe se pata hai uska answer dene ke liye aap answer par click kare or apne answer ko likhe or submit karde bus apka answer submit hogya.Man lijiye aapke diye gye sawal ke jawab ko 1000 logo ne dekha hai inme se kam se kam 100 log aapki site par visit jarur karenge aap meri is week ki report dekhiye.Yaha meri pichle week ki Quora ki report hai jisme mere sawalo ko 1043 logo ne dekha hai jisme se 50% logo ne mere sawalo ko padne ke bad meri website par visit kiya hai.is tarah aap apne site ke traffic ko doguna kar sakte hai ye ek aajmaya hua tarika hai jo 100% working hai jitne jyda aap sawalo ke jawab denge utne jyada apko apne sawalo par view milenge or apki site par traffic milega.To is tarah ham apni site ke traffic ko increase kar sakte hai Me hi nhi India ke janemane Digital marketing expert Neil Patel ka bhi yahi kahna hai ki aap Quora se apni site ke traffic ko 35% tak bada sakte hai.To ye thi hamri aaj ki post agar aapko post pasand aaye to apne friends se share kare or agar apka koi sawal ho to Naukri Delhi Chandigarh Uttar Pradesh Bihar Haryana Himachal Pradesh Madhya Pradesh Punjab Rajasthan Private Naukri Delhi Chandigarh Uttar Pradesh Bihar Haryana Himachal Pradesh Madhya Pradesh Punjab Rajasthan Freshers Health Hindi Se Help Technology aur Health Ki Jankari HomeBlogger ki jankariBlogger Blog Me Youtube Subscribe Button Kaise Add Kare Blogger ki jankari Blogger Blog Me Youtube Subscribe Button Kaise Add Kare [ Two Methods ] By Raghav Tripathi -November 24, 2017 7 592 Share on Facebook Tweet on Twitter Hello Friends Mera Naam Sultan Hai me apni site Blognetbook.com website par Blogging, Web design, Blog Widgets, Seo, Tutorials Hindi me share karta hun.
Par ek Blogger Banna chate hai.Agar aap ek Blogger se shaadi karne ja rahe hai to aap unhi se puch sakte hai ki Blogging kaise karte hai, wo aapko achi se samja dege To chaliye ab aate hai apne main Point par or jante hai, kya kya faide hai ek Blogger se shaadi karne se..Blogger Se Shaadi Karne ke Faide in Hindi#1: Kahi Se Bhi Kaam Kar Sakte HaiJo Blogger hai unko sirf Apne Laptop/Computer or Internet ki jarurat hoti hai, or ye Dinuya Bhar me kahi bhi mil jayega, matlab wo apna blogging ka kaam duniya ke kisi bhi kone se kar sakte hai.To Isse Faida ye hai, Unko aapse Dur jane ki jarurat nahi padegi, wo chahe to Ghar me bhi apna Office setup kar sakte hai.#2:Good UnderstandingBlogger ki Dusro ko samajne ki Power ek dusre person se jada hoti hai, q ki wo bhut se anjan logo se deal karta hai, jinko wo nahi janta.. aese me har trha ke logo se Blogger ka pala padta rheta hai, or unko kaise handle karna hai wo achi se janta hai.Blogger ke Blog par comment aate hai, to ache comment ke sath sath bure bhi kabhi kabhi aa jate hai, par aese me wo ye samajne ki kosis karta hai ki isne aesa q kaha, kya galti ki mene or wo usko sudharte hai.. Aur logo ki trha Dusro par blame nahi karta.To agar aap kuch baat kahege to aapka Blogger Partner aapki bato ko achi se samjega, or aapki baat ka bura nahi manega.#3: Good ListenerBlogger ache listener bhi hote hai, wo har ek ki baat ko achi se sunte hai or samajte hai, to aese me aap bhale ghanto apni story apne Blogger partner ko sunate rahe wo aapse bore nahi hoge.Aap kuch bhi unse kahege to wo aapki baat ko achi se sunege, or ye to har koi chata hai ki wo agar kisi se kuch khe rahe hai to wo unki baat dhiyan se sune.#4:SupportiveJo Blogger hai wo supportive bhi bhut hote hai, kisi ki bhi Help ki baat ho to jitna unse possible hota hai wo help karte hai.. or dusro ko bhi sath lekar chalte hai.aese me agar aapka Partner Blogger hai to wo aapko aapke har ache kaam me support karege or Motive bhi taki aap apne uss kaam ko or achi se kar paye.Aapke Kaam me wo support karege uske piche ka ek karan ye bhi hai ki wo achi se jante hai passion ka kaam karne me kitni khusi milti hai, to agar aapka koi passion hai or aap wo karna chate hai to aapko pura support milege taki aap bhi khus raho.#5: Helping Naturejo Blogging karte hai unka nature automatic aesa ho jata hai ki wo sabki Help karna pasand karte hai, to aese me aap to unke Life Partner rahege to aapki Help ke liye to wo hamesa teyar rahege hi.#6:Problem SolverProblem to sabki life me aati rheti hai, par jo un problem ki baja se tut naa jaye wo hota hai asli insan, or ye khubi ek blogger me kut-kut ke bhari hoti hai.Dusre kamo ki trha Blogging me bhi kabhi kabhi dikkat aa jati hai, par wo un problem se bhagta nahi hai or unka solution search karke usko sahi karta hai.to aese me Life me koi bhi Problem aai to wo unko sahi tarike se Solve kar sakte hai.#7:PassionateAapne 3 idiots Movie to dekhi ho hogi, jisme hame ye sikh milti hai ki hame apne passion kaa kaam karna chaiye jab hi ham khus rhe sakte hai or kuch badiya kar sakte hai.Jo Blogger hai unka yahi passion hota hai or wo usko apne full potential se karte hai, to isse unko blogging me to acha result milta hi hai, sath sath wo aapko bhi apne passion ka kaam karne se nahi rokege.#8:Self DependBlogger Self depend hote hai, wo jo bhi karte hai khud ke dam par karte hai..#9: Every Time HappyBlogger hamesa khus rhete hai, ab iska matlab ye nahi ki dusre log jo blogging nahi karte wo khus nahi rhete.. khene ka matlab hai jisko jo kaam karne me khusi milti hai agar wo wahi kaam kare to wo hamesa khus rheta hai.To agar aap aese insan ke sath rahege jo hamesa khus rheta hai to sidhi si baat hai aap bhi khus rahege.#10:TravellingBlogger ko Travel karna or nai nai jagha ghumna, or adventure karna bhut pasand hota hai, to aese me Life ke or bhi jo maje hai wo aap unke sath le sakte hai.Blogging or Internet Marketing ke Event hote rhete hai, to agar wo unko attend karne ja rahe hai to aap bhi unke sath jaa sakte hai, aese me kaam ke sath sath Holiday bhi ho jayega.#11: TimeBlogging ek Business ki trha hai, to isme wo hamare upar hai ham kis time kaam kare..To aese me wo aapko pura time de payege, q ki unke upar koi dabab nahi rahega ki unko itne time kaam karna hi hai.#12: Apni Galti Maan lete haiJo blogger hote hai, unme upar batai khubiya hoti hi hai, to aese me agar kabhi aapke bich kuch misunderstanding hui or to wo achi se uss condition ko samaj lege.. or agar unki galti hui to Sorry bolne me hichkichate nahi hai.#13: Special SurprisesSurprises to sabko pasand hote hi hai, or sab chate hai ki koi unke liyeSurprise plan kare.. to aese me agar aapke partner blogger hai to iske chances jada ho jate hai.Blogger Internet par kuch naa kuch search karte rhete hai, ye to aap jante hi hoge to aese me iski bhut jada possibility hai unko aapke liye kuch pasand aa jaye kuch search karte hue or wo bina aapko bataye aapke liye order karde..#14: Technology or Internet ka Acha KnowledgeAb ye Point to wese muje batane ki jarurat nahi hai, q ki ye to unka kaam hi hai, to aese me unko iski achi jankari to hogi hi..Par isse aapko bhi bhut faida milega.. Q ki agar aapko Internet or Technology ki jada jankari nahi hai to bhi aapko tension lene ki jarurat nahi hai, aapka koi bhi kaam ho aasani se ho jayega.#15: Work TogetherAap chahe to aap bhi unke sath kaam kar sakte hai, q ki blogging me aesa nahi hai ki koi padhai jaruri ho.Jisko thoda bhut Internet chalana aata ho, wo aasani se apni website bana kar blogging kar sakte hai, or agar aapke partner hi Blogger rahege to aapko to koi problem hi nahi aayegi.To aap apne Talent ko duniya se share kar payege or usse thodi bhut earing to aaram se kar hi sakte hai, jisse aap apne Blogger Partner ko Suprise Gift de sake #16: Ready for EverythingHar Chij ke liye hamesa teyar, agar aapne kabhi Movie ka kaha to wo turant haa bol dege, q ki jo ek blogger hai uska sabse phela aasaul hi hota hai Life ko Injoy karna, to agar unka uss time kuch kaam bhi hota to wo usko night me kar lege.

yoga motapa wajan kam kaise kare Motapa Kam Kaise Kare Weight Lose Gharelu Nushke In Hindi 1# Ajwain Pani Se Vajan Kam Kaise Kare Ajwain ek best gherelu ilaaj hai pet ki koi bhi samsya hoto hame sabse pehle ajwain yaad ata hai ham ajwain ka upyog karte hai dosto ajwain pet ki deggset ke saaath saath pet ki sabhi preshaniyo ko door karta hai aur ajwain hamare pet ki acidity aur sabhi problems ko door kardeta hai Ajwain se ham pet ki samsya ke saath hi ajwain ke upyog se mota pa kam kar sakte hai pet ki charbi kam kaise kare simple iske liye aap ye gharelu nushka ajamaye ajwain ke paani ko roj subha sawere pinese pet ki charbi kam hojati hai Ajwain drink kaise banaye ajwain drink ka upyog kaise kare sabse pehle 25 ya 50 garam ajwain ko ek gilaas paani me daley raat me aur saari raat bhigne chod dey jab subha hojaye ajwaine ke pani wale gass lekar use chaanley aur pani me ek chamach shahed milakar pile Dosto is upaaye ko hame 50 days tak karna hai yafir kam se kam 35 days tak to kare ise saath aapke body ko iska acha faida bhi milta hai isliye is ko follow kare 3# Dhaniya Aur Nimbu Hara Dhanaiya ek parkar se bohut faide mand hai aur ye ek parkar ka natural anti oxidant hai aur nimbu ke bareme to aapko pata hi hoga nimbu me vitamin c paya jata hai jo hamare sharir ki gandagi bahar karta hai aur hame health fit fine banaye rakhta hai] Dhaniya aur nimbu drink kaise banaye dosto *Ek war me Minimum 1000 add kar sakte hai or Maximum 10 lakh#3: ZebPay me paise add hone ke baad Bitcoin kharidne ke liye Buy ki button par click kare.#4: Ab kitne rupee ke Bitcoin kharidna chate hai wo dale, Pure paise ka kharidna ho to All select kare.Bitcoin jsitime kharidege us time jitni bhi Bitcoin ki kimat hogi uske hisab se aapne jitne rupee ke kharide hai utne ke Bitcoin mil jayege..Zebpay me Bitcoin Sell kaise kareSell karna bhut aasan hai, Simple jo Sell ki button hai uspar click kare.aapko kitne rupee ke bitcoin sell karna hai wo dale, aap chahe to pure bhi sell kar sakte hai.Sell karne ke baad jo paise hai wo aapke Zebpay me aajayega.. or agar aap un paiso ko Bank me transfer karna chate hai to withdraw par click karke kar sakte hai jo 24 hours me aapke bank account me aa jayege.Bitcoin se Paise Kaise KamayeBitcoin se paise kamana chate hai to simple aapko usme paise invest karna hai or jab uska rate badh jaye to usko sell karke paise kama sakte hai.At Last: BitcoinKaise Kharidna hai or Bechna hai India me wo to mene bata diya hai or kaise aap usse paise kama sakte hai wo bhi aap samaj gaye hoge, par fir bhi ho sakta hai aapka koi sabal ho to aap niche comment karke jarur puche.Me aapko batadu mene ek mahine phele 3lakh ke Bitcoin kharide the jo abhi 4.5Lakh ke ho gaye.. to ab aap calculate kar lijiye kitni speed se kitne paise kama sakte hai.Bitcoin me sabse main baat ye hai ye kisi ke control me nahi hai to iska jo Rate hai wo iski demand or mining ke hisab se upar niche hota hai.. par kuch expert ka khena hai saal ke akhri tak 6 lakh rate hone ki sambhamna hai.Author Note: Mene aapko Bitcoin kaise kharidna or bechna hai wo bata diya hai, ab aap jitne ka bhi kharidna chahe kharid sakte hai, par iski koi conform nahi khe sakte ki kam nahi hota.. to agar aapka koi nuksan hota hai to uske jimmedar aap khud hoge.Me aapko suggest karuga aapke pass agar extra paise hai to wo Bitcoin me lagaye or thode lambe time tak ke liye lagaye.. Long Time me Rate badega hi itna to pakka hai..Agar aap isme paise laga rahe hai to apni itni chamta rakhe ki agar wo pure paise dub jaye to bhi aapko koi problem naa aaye, wese aesa hoga to nahi.. par Risk utna hi lena chaiye jitne me ham sabal paye.Hope aapko meri di hui jankari pasand aai hogi, baki aapke koi bhi sabal hai to comment me most welcome.. &nbsp;keyword me kayi parkar hote hai agar aap nhi jante to ek bar googlre me search kare aur apne sawal ka jabab paye keyword matlub jaise abhi maine post me kaha blog ki seo setting kaise kare ye yek keyword huwa &nbsp;dosto&nbsp; seo ka dusra naam keywords hai I mean&nbsp; seo me 70% bhag keywords ka hi hota haiAgar aapko seo me keywords ki achi jankari hai ki post me high quality keywords kaise aur kaha place kare&nbsp;&nbsp; keyword density kya hai kitni percentage honi chahiye ek post me kitne keyword use kare etc&nbsp; google ko sabse pehle ye jana hota hai ki aapki post kis liye hai I mean post topic kya hai iske liye sabse jaruri hai Post Me Keywords Kaha Place Kare 1.Post Title me keywords ad kareAapki post ka title jiha&nbsp; post ka title attractive seo friendly banaye kyuki jab bhi aapki post google&nbsp; index karta hai sabse pehle wo aapka title dekhta hai ki kis topic&nbsp; par aapki post based hai taki jab bhi koi visitor aapki taraha apke topic wala title search kare&nbsp; tabhi aapki site us page me aaye agar aap title hi nhi dalenge to google konse page par aapki post show karega aap sochsakte ho isliye post ka title me jarur aapna ek focus keyword ad kare example&nbsp; aap post likhrahe ho ki blog website kaise banaye to ab post ka title bhi yehi chune2.Post Pragraph Me Keyword DaalePost ki paragraph me keywords ad place kare dosto keywords ki stretgy bhi simple hai aapko apne post ke paragraph me keywords ad karne chahiye&nbsp; sabse3 pehle first paragraph&nbsp; ke first line ya second line me apna ek focus keyword ad jarur kare taki koi vyakti aapke post me jo keyword hai use realeted kuch search karta hai tabhi aapki ye wali post jarur aaye&nbsp;&nbsp; 1st&nbsp; paragraph me keywords use kare&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 2nd paragraph me keyword use kare and next last wale me apna ek focus keyword ad jarur kare3.Post Image Me Keyword Ad KarePost ke saath aap jo post me image use kar rahe hai use bhi seo friendly banana jarur hai isliye mai aapko short me batata hu ki image ko seo friendly kaise banaye post ki image ko seo friendly kaise banaye &nbsp;&nbsp;jab aap free site se image lete hai ya&nbsp; khud se banate hai tab image ka rename jo hota hai use aapko change karna hota hai usme apne post ke keyword ad karne hote hai jaise&nbsp; is post ka title rename change karne ke bad aapki image seo friendly hochuki hai 4.Post Description Me Keywords daley&nbsp;Post editor ke side me jo description hota hai woha par aapko aapki post ke bareme kuch likhna hota hai jaise ki isme kya jankari hai etc aur&nbsp; is description me aapko apna ek keyword use karna hota hai taki aapki site postsearch me kamal karske &nbsp;yeha par apna ek focus keyword dalne ke bad save kare5.Post Heading MeBlog post me jab ham post likhte hai us samye hame heading ka upyog karna chahiye jise hame search engine google ke 1st page par rank milne ka mouka milta hai&nbsp; h1 to default title ke template me pehle se hota hai iski jarurat nhi hai agar nhi hai to aap post me khud se use kare h2 ka use kare&nbsp; aur insab headings me apna keyword ad kare5.Permalink Me Keyword Use KarePermalink kya hai&nbsp; ) Ab aage badne se phele me manta hu aapne Domain or Hosting kharidli hai or aapke pass Cpanel ka Login ID password bhi hai jo aapke email par aaya hoga hosting kharidne ke baad. Chaliye ab dekh lete hai kaise 5 minute me WordPress kaise install karte hai. WordPress install karne ke phele kuch setting hai jo karni hai.. Domain ka NameServer Change karna hai. Hosting Cpanel me Domain add karna hai agar wo main domain nahi hai to. Ye kaise karna hai, uske ware meWordPress Install karne ki step by step Process me bata chuka hu, Please aap Iss Link par jakar Part 1 ko follow kare.. uske baad wapas iss article par aaye. To ab aapne Domain ka Nameserver Change kar diya hai or domain bhi Cpanel me add kar diya hai. WordPress Auto Install kaise karte hai Ab aapko Cpanel meSoftaculous Apps Installer dikhega, uspar click karna hai. Ab New Page aayega, usme WordPress Install par click karna hai. Ab WordPress Install karne ke liye, Information Daalkar Install karna hai.. Website www ya without www chate hai wo select kare, Yaha https select karne ka bhi option hai agar aapne SSL install kiya huaa hai Domain me phele se to select kar sakte hai. Apna Domain Select kare, jispar aap WordPress Install karna chate hai.. Main Site banana chate hai to isko khali rhene de, or agar Directory me WordPress install karna chate hai to wo dali. Website Ka Name dale. Website ki Tagline (Discription) dale. Agar aap Muntipal WordPress site ek hi jagha manage karna chate hai to isko select kare.. warna isko tik naa kare. Website ke liye USERNAME Dale, phele se admin hoga.. usko hata kar kuch bhi aesa rakhe jo koi aasani se andaja naa laga sake. Password set kare, ye bhi aesa jo koi andaja naa laga sake.. (Key ke icon par click karke strong password bana sakte hai, uske baad username or password kahi save karke rakhle..) Website User ke liye Email Dale. WordPress ki Language select kare.. Limit Login Attempted par tik kare, jisse koi 3 war galat password dalege to wo IP block ho jayegi, ye security ke liye acha hai.. aap chahe to baad me bhi kar sakte hai. Advanced Option me kuch or setting milegi, wo aap chahe to change kar sakte hai ya jesi hai wesi hi rhene de.. Puri Detail fill karne ke baad Install ki button par click kare. Ab WordPress Install hone lagega, isme jada se jada 2 minute lagege. WordPress Install hone ke baad aesa message show hoga.. Ab aap apni website open karke dekh sakte hai URL par click karke.. Website ko manage karne ke liye uske deshboard me login karna padega, jiske liye aapki jo website hai uske samne wp-admin likh kar open karna padega.. uske baad jo Username or Password set kiya tha wordpress install karte time wo daal kar login karna hai. WordPress Deshboard me login karke ke baad aesa dikhega.. To jese ki aapne dekha, Simple 2-3 steps me WordPress site badi aasani se bana sakte hai, isme agar aapko koi doubt hai ya kahi kuch sabal ho to aap Comment karke jarur puche. WordPress Install karne ke baad kuch Important setting hai jo aapko karni hai uske baad hi aapko WordPress site ko aage use karna hai. WordPress ki bhut si Jankari phele hi me share kar chuka hu, wo aap search kar sakte hai site par.. or agar kuch aesa ho jo aapko nahi mile to aap comment karke puch sakte hai. Ussd Code for idea All Code Idea USSD codes ki madad se aap apne Number ka Balance, Data, SMS, Calls, Gprs data bagera pata kar sakte ho. (u'www.hindimehelp.com', u'/hack-ka-karan/', u'HMH Hack Kaise Hui or Kya Badi Galti hui | Hindi Me HelpHomeBloggingBloggerWordPressBloggingSEOGuest PostsSocial MediaFacebookTwitterYouTubeGoogleWhatsappSocial NetworkInternetImportant WebsiteToolsInternetMake MoneyMotivationalMoreComputerMobileFestivalHMHSearchHindi Me HelpHomeBloggingBloggerWordPressBloggingSEOGuest PostsSocial MediaFacebookTwitterYouTubeGoogleWhatsappSocial NetworkInternetImportant WebsiteToolsInternetMake MoneyMotivationalMoreComputerMobileFestivalHMHHomeBloggingHMH Hack Kaise Hui or Kya Badi Galti huiBloggingHindi Me HelpHMH Hack Kaise Hui or Kya Badi Galti huiBy Rohit Mewada - July 3, 201790Facebook Twitter Google+ WhatsApp PinterestHello Bloggers, Hope aap sab badiya hoge, or aapki Website bhi badia hogi, or jo HMH ke sath huaa, wo aapki site ke sath kabhi nahi hoga, HMH kaise Hack hui or kya galti rahi meri wo sab me aapko is post me batane wala hu, taki aap ye galti naa kare.HMH Hack hui thi, ye sayad aapko pata hoga, or ye pure 31 Hours Down rahi, jisme mera sirf site se jo earning hoti thi sirf wo nuksan nahi huaa, uske sath mera bhut sa nuksan huaa jiske ware me abhi me bataoga.HMH Hack Kaise HuiHMH Hack hone ka karan tha muje VPS ki sahi jankari naa hona or uske sath hi usme kuch Bug hone ke karan hacker ko uske through hack karne me aasani hona.Meri jo hosting thi wo VPS Plan tha, jiska Monthly charge 6,000 tha, jisme muje memory or baki jo sab chije chaiye thi wo to mil rahi thi par security ke mamle me hosting company ka khena tha ki ye bhi aapko bhi karna tha jo muje samaj nahi aaya.Or sabse main baat ham normal hosting lete hai to hosting company ke pass uska backup rheta hai, par VPS Hosting ka Backup bhi hame hi set karna padta hai jo mene nahi kiya.. to muje mera purana backup bhi nahi mila hosting account se.VPS me hame hi puri setting karni padti hai, par muje uska jada knowledge nahi hoge ke karan mene usko sahi se set nahi kiya.. or usski ka fayda hacker ne uthaya.Hacker ko jese hi access mila site ka, usme sabse phele to database ko pura phele barbad kiya uske baad delete kar diya, uske baad site ki jo files thi, unko bhi pura barbad kar diya..To ab condition ye thi, me uss hosting se apni site ko sahi nahi kar sakta tha, to ab mera sabse phela target tha ki kaise bhi karke muje Post ka backup mil jaye..Iske liye mene Developer se contact kiya par unko bhi kuch samaj nahi aa raha tha ki kaise kya kare, par ye kaho meri kismat achi thi, jo mene 2 din phele hi database ka backup liya tha, offline download karne ke liye par download to nahi kiya uss din par wo mene main directory se nikal par bahar daal diya tha uska Zip file..Hack hone ke baad usko download karte uske phele hosting company se meri hosting account ko block kar diya, q ki VPS me kuch aese action bhi liye gaye jiske karan hosting account ko vlock kardiya gaya.. or sath me mera VPS server bhi down ho gaya.ab mene hosting company se contact kiya, ki muje kaise bhi karke wo data chaiye.. to unhone kaha ham puri kosis karege.. or jese hi server sahi huaa mene sabse phele database ki file download ki..Meri Sabse Badi GaltiAb baat aati hai meri kaha galti hui or mere pass backup q nahi tha,Bhut se mere friends ne mere pass call kiya, message kiye.. or FB Group me bhi sabse apni taraf se puri help karne ki kosis ki..Par me aapko bata du, mene kya galti ki thi, mene Updraft plugin se backup set kar rakha tha, to Backup direct DropBox me ho jata tha.. par yaha mene ek bat ka dhiyan nahi diya ki site ka size 1 GB se jada ho gaya hai.dropbox me hame 2 GB free space miltra hai or HMH ka size 1.2GB tha or mene site ke 2 backup dropbox me save rahe aesi setting kar rakhi thi, to uske baja se dropbox me sabhi file backup ho rahi thi, sirf database ki file ka backup nahi ho raha tha.. or mene iska dhiyan nahi rakha ye meri sabse badi galti thi.Mere Pass VPS me kuch error ke message aaye the, jisme muje alert kiya gaya tha ki kuch aesi activity mere account me ho rahi hai jo sahi nahi hai.. par mene uss baat ko jada series nai liya, nahi to muje ussi time hosting company se contact karna tha.Hack hone ke baad condition ye thi, mere pass database ka 1 mahine purana backup tha, files ka pura backup dropbox me tha, or mera VPS server down ho gaya tha.yahi karan tha ki HMH 31 ghanto tak down rahi..Ab me uss hosting company se aage continue bhi nahi karna chata tha.. q ki me security ka apne se khayal to rakh sakta hu, par muje aesi hosting chaiye thi jisme hosting company bhi uska pura khayal rakhe.Jese hi muje HMH ka Pura Backup mila mene usko turant dusri hosting me host karke HMH ko Live kiya.

Jo Code hota hai usko ham jese hi Mobile me camera se scan karte hai us code me jo bhi message hota hai to aa jata hai.QR Code ka Kya Kya Istmaal haiAbhi ke time me QR Code ka bhut si jagha use ho raha hai, Q ki ham sab jaante hai Mobile to har ek ke pass hai to agar hame kuch information kisi ke mobile me jaldi se deta hai to wo ham QR Code ki madad se kar sakte haiYe kuch Chije jo ham QR Code se kar sakte haiBookMark Link (website ki link jisko scan karne par wo bookmark ho jaye)Contact (Apna Contact ka QR Code bana sakte hai jisko scan karne par hamare contacty ki detail turant aa jati hai)Email ID (Code ko scan karne par hamari set ki hui ID aa jati hai jispar direct email send karne ka option aa jata hai)GEO Location (Location set kar sakte hai, to jese hi fir code ko scan kiya jata hai map me wo location open ho jati hai)Phone (Mobile Number add kar sakte hai jisko scan karte hi call lag jati hai us number par)SMS (Mobile Number or Message set kar sakte hai, to jese hi koi code ko scan karega wo sms send ho jayega us number par)Text (Agar koi message display karna hai ya aesi koi bhi jankari jo sirf text me dikhe to wo bhi kar sakte hai.

software engineering karne ka kitna badiya scope hai &nbsp;so&nbsp; software engineering karne ke bohut faaide hai&nbsp; jise ham post me batayenge ki kaise kaha konsa job aapko konse courses par miljata hai Software Engineering Kya Hoti HaiSoftware engineering kya hai ?

2.BruteForce Attack Se Instagram Hack Kaise Kare Mostly sabhi password is method se koi ek hacker tod sakta hai,Ab aap soch rahe honge ki maine bola tha ki agar aap sahi se spacial character use karte hai to koi bhi password nhi tod payega.To dosto pura sentence padhiye maine sirf ye kaha ki sabhi password bruteforce attack se toot sakte hai lekin kitni der me tootenge ye nhi bataya ,to aapko bata du ki agar aapke passowrd me simple character hai ,numbers hai albhabat hai to bruteforce attack se asani se aapka passowrd crack kar liya jayega lekin isme bhi kam se kam 1 ghante ka time lagega ,aur socho agar aapka passowrd strong hai usme spacial character jaise @#$%^& ka use hua hai to brute force attack se ye bhi password toot jayega lekin lagbhag 200 years me ,to aap samjh gaye honge ki strong password ko tod pana nearly impossible hai.

? Matlab jinhone phele Bitcoin kharide the unki to chadi chadi hai, par agar kisi ne abhi tak nahi kharide hai to bhi koi baat nahi wo abhi bhi kharid sakte hai. Abhi 1 Bitcoin ki kimat 4.510Lakh hai. aesa jaruri nahi ham pura ek Bitcoin hi kharida jaye, ham unka kuch hissa bhi kharid sakte hai jisko santosi khete hai.. Minimum 1000 rupee ke bitcoin kharid sakte hai.. Bitcoin Buy n Sell kaise kare India me Bitcoin kharidne ke bhut se website hai par konsa website sahi hai konsa nahi ye samaj pana thoda muskil hai.. par me jis website ke ware me bata raha hu aap unme bharosa kar sakte hai q ki me usko 1 saal se use kar raha hu, jiska naam hai Zebpay. Bitcoin ke Top Website jinki madad se Bitcoin buy-Sell, Trade kar sakte hai uski jankari yaha hai, me aapko suggest karuga aap un sabhi site par apna account banaye, or jab bhi aap kharidna chahe jaha sabse sasta ho waha se kharide.. Chaliye Dekh lete hai Kaise Zebpay se Bitcoin ko Buy n Sell karte hai or kaise iske jariye paise kama sakte hai. Sabse phele aapko Zebpay ka App Install karna hai, uske liye aap niche ki button par click karke download kare.. jisse aapko 100 extra bonus bhi mil jayega bitcoin kharidte time. Downlaod Zebpay Note: Agar Zebpay me account banate time referral code mage to REF74812203 jarur dale jab hi aapko 100 ka bonus milega. Zebpay App Download karne ke baad aapko apna account banana hai, Account banate time apni sahi sahi detail dale.. agar account banane me koi problem aaye to aap comment karke puch sakte hai. Important Note: Account banate time jo PIN set kare wo yaad rakhe, Q ki PIN 3 war galat dalne par account 24 hours ke liye Block ho jata hai. Account ban jane ke baad aapko apna account verify karna hoga.. Zebpay Account Verification kaise hoga #1: Sabse phele setting me ja kar verification par jaye, uske baad apne PAN Card ki detail submit kare. PAN Card Detail submit karne ke 24 hours me PAN Card verify ho jayega. *Agar aapka PAN Card nahi hai to banwa lijiye, ek hafte me aaram se ban jayega.. #2: PAN Card Verify hone ke baad Bank Detail dalni hai, yaha jo Bank account Name hai wo PAN Card me hai wahi hona chaiye.. agar alag naam hoga to add nahi hoga. #3: Apna Address Verify karna hai, iske sath yahaAadhaar Cardka Photo bhi upload karna hoga. Iss trha zebpay ka account verify hota hai, account ko puri trha se verify hone me 48 hours tak lag sakte hai. Account puri trha se verify karne ke baad aap teyar hai Bitcoin kharidne wa bachne ke liye. Zebpay me Bitcoin kaise Kharide Zebpay se Bitcoin kharidne ke liye sabse phele aapko usme paise add karna hai.. uske baad un paiso se bitcoin ko kharida ja sakta hai. #1: Zebpay me Paise Add karne ke liye Deposit ki button par click kare. #2: kitna amount add karna chate hai wo dale.. Deposit karne ke 2 option hai.. NEFT ya Net Banking NetBanking se paise add karne par 30 minute me Zebpay me add ho jate hai or agar NEFT se karte hai to 24 hours me paise add hoge. *Netbanking ussi account se hogi jis Name se PAN Card lagaya hai. *Ek war me Minimum 1000 add kar sakte hai or Maximum 10 lakh #3: ZebPay me paise add hone ke baad Bitcoin kharidne ke liye Buy ki button par click kare. #4: Ab kitne rupee ke Bitcoin kharidna chate hai wo dale, Pure paise ka kharidna ho to All select kare. Bitcoin jsitime kharidege us time jitni bhi Bitcoin ki kimat hogi uske hisab se aapne jitne rupee ke kharide hai utne ke Bitcoin mil jayege.. Zebpay me Bitcoin Sell kaise kare Sell karna bhut aasan hai, Simple jo Sell ki button hai uspar click kare. aapko kitne rupee ke bitcoin sell karna hai wo dale, aap chahe to pure bhi sell kar sakte hai. Sell karne ke baad jo paise hai wo aapke Zebpay me aajayega.. or agar aap un paiso ko Bank me transfer karna chate hai to withdraw par click karke kar sakte hai jo 24 hours me aapke bank account me aa jayege. Bitcoin se Paise Kaise Kamaye Bitcoin se paise kamana chate hai to simple aapko usme paise invest karna hai or jab uska rate badh jaye to usko sell karke paise kama sakte hai. At Last: BitcoinKaise Kharidna hai or Bechna hai India me wo to mene bata diya hai or kaise aap usse paise kama sakte hai wo bhi aap samaj gaye hoge, par fir bhi ho sakta hai aapka koi sabal ho to aap niche comment karke jarur puche. Me aapko batadu mene ek mahine phele 3lakh ke Bitcoin kharide the jo abhi 4.5Lakh ke ho gaye.. to ab aap calculate kar lijiye kitni speed se kitne paise kama sakte hai. Bitcoin me sabse main baat ye hai ye kisi ke control me nahi hai to iska jo Rate hai wo iski demand or mining ke hisab se upar niche hota hai.. par kuch expert ka khena hai saal ke akhri tak 6 lakh rate hone ki sambhamna hai. Author Note: Mene aapko Bitcoin kaise kharidna or bechna hai wo bata diya hai, ab aap jitne ka bhi kharidna chahe kharid sakte hai, par iski koi conform nahi khe sakte ki kam nahi hota.. to agar aapka koi nuksan hota hai to uske jimmedar aap khud hoge. Me aapko suggest karuga aapke pass agar extra paise hai to wo Bitcoin me lagaye or thode lambe time tak ke liye lagaye.. Long Time me Rate badega hi itna to pakka hai.. Agar aap isme paise laga rahe hai to apni itni chamta rakhe ki agar wo pure paise dub jaye to bhi aapko koi problem naa aaye, wese aesa hoga to nahi.. par Risk utna hi lena chaiye jitne me ham sabal paye. Hope aapko meri di hui jankari pasand aai hogi, baki aapke koi bhi sabal hai to comment me most welcome.. Info:Bitcoin ke FounderSatoshi Nakamotohai jo Asliyat me kon hai koi nahi janta.. jo Duniya ke Top Amiro me 247 number par aate hai jinhone aaj hi din 2010 me Bitcoin banai thi. Keyword search karne ke liye aap Google Keyword Planner ka use kar sakte hai jo bilkul free hai, uske sath sath aap Google Search ka bhi use kar sakte hai, jisme automatic jo suggestion aate hai usse andaja laga sakte hai log kaise search karte hai.Keywords 2 trha ke hote haiShort KeywordLong Tail KeywordShort Keyword: Ham jab post likhne ke liye koi keyword select karte hai to usme jo hamara main target hota hai jisko hame rank karna hai, agar wo main topic hi hai to wo hamara keyword hoga.Short Keyword me dikkat ye hai, usme computation bhut jada rheta hai, or agar phele se badiya tarike se achi website par diya huaa hai to aapki post rank hi nahi kar payegi.. par agar aap short keyword ko bhi rank kara de to aapko traffic achi mil sakti hai.Long Tail Keyword: koi topic hai jiske sath kuch extra keyword bhi add ho jaye to wo long tail keyword hota hai.

| Adword Kya hai Hindi me" href="https://www.hindimehelp.com/what-is-google-adwords-hindi-me/">Adword jo Adsense ka ulta hai, matlab agar kisi ko apna koi Advertisement karana hai to wo Google ko paise dekar apna advertise karate hai Adword ke jariye.. to iss trha Google ke pass ad dikhane ke liye content aata hai. Ab jinki Website ya Youtube channel hai to Google Adsense ke jariye wo ad apni Site or Youtube Video par lagate hai.. to aese me jo ad aate hai usse traffic unki site par jati hai jinhone google ko advertise karne ke liye paise diye the. Jitne Bhi Ad hote hai uska 32% commsion Google apnepass rakhta hai or baki ka 68% wo Publisher ko deta hai jinki site par wo ad dikha tha.. Ab aapko ye to clear ho gaya hoga, Google ne apna sirf Program banaya hai jo ads hai wo koi or dete hai or unko dikhate koi or hai.. par iss puri process ko manage karne ka kaam hai google ka. Google Adsense se Paise Kaise Kamaye Agar aapko Google Adsense se paise kamana hai to aapke pass kuch aesa hona chaiye jispar aap unke ad laga sake.. iske liye aapki koi website honi chaiye ya youtube channel.. Website Kaise Banate hai Youtube channel kaise banate hai Agar aapke Pass ye hai to aap Adsense me account bana kar Apply kar sakte hai, par yaha ek baat jo aapko dhiyan rakhna hai.. Adsense ki Policy bhut khathin hai.. me aapko suggest karuga aap Adsense account bana kar apply karne se phele unki policy ko achi se jarur padhe. Google Adsense Terms and Conditions in hindi Google Adsense Ad Placement Policies in Hindi Inke aalawa mene ek Post likhi hai, jisme mene Adsense ki Puri Jankari or uske sabhi Sabalo ke jabab diya hai to agar aapka koi sabal hai to phele aap uss post ko read kare, or agar uske aalawa bhi koi sabal ho to aap comment karke puch sakte hai. Adsense Account Apply kab kare Adsense account banana simple account banane jitna aasan nahi hai, q ki account ko approve karene ke liye hamare pass kuch aesa content hona chaiye jike liye wo hamara adsense account ko approve kare.. Ab ya to wo Youtube channel ho sakta hai ya koi website. Website ke liye Adsense Kab Apply kare: Agar koi website hai, to sabse phele to uspar badiya content, Badiya Design or badiya Navigation hona chaiye taki koi bhi usko achi se chala sake.. uske baad kuch visitor bhi hona jaruri hai taki site ka review jaldi ho or account jaldi approve ho. Agar aap Website ke liye apply karne wale hai toGoogle Adsense Approve Kaise Kare Blog/Website ke liye wali guide jarur read kare. Youtube ke liye Adsense kab apply kare: Youtube par phele to Channel bana kar Channel verify karke turant apply kar sakte the.. par ab Channel par total 10,000+ Views hona jaruri hai, uske sath channel Good Stending me hona chaiye jab Adsense connect kar sakte hai.. Youtube se Adsense Kaise connect karte hai uski jankari aapko yaha mil jayegi. Adsense se Earning Kaise Hoti hai Abhi tak aap ye to jaan gaye hoge, ki Adsense ek Ad network hai, jisko join karke ham apni Youtube Video or Website par Ads dikha sakte hai or unki madad se earning kar sakte hai. Adsense se jo Earning hoti hai wo ad se hoti hai, or ads bhi Alag alag trha ke hai jisme Link Ad, Display Ad or Video Ad samil hai. Ab hota ye hai, jese hamne apni website par Ad lagaya hai to agar koi hamari website ko open karege to unko wo ad dikhega.. or agar wo unki pasand ka huaa to wo uspar click bhi karege.. usse hame paise milte hai.. Tikh issi trha Youtube Video ka bhi hai. Ek click par kitne paise milte hai wo fix nahi hai, q ki har ad ka alag rate hota hai, fir bhi aap andaja laga sakte hai ki aapko kis hisab se mil raha hai, mene bataya hai Adsense 1000 Views par kitni earning hoti hai. Google Adsense se Paise Kaise Milte hai ab baat aati hai jo hamari Earning hui hai Adsense se wo hame kaise milegi. Google Adsense har mahine ki 21 tarikh ko payment send karte hai, or jo minimum payment hai wo hai $100.. matlab agar isse kam earning huaa to Next month me add hoke aayegi. Adsense Payment lene ke liye hame phele Adsense Account Verify karna hota hai, Adsense account verification ke liye hamare Address par Adsense me $10 Income hone ke baad ek Latter send kiya jata hai..

Mistake 38:Unrelated Content add karna post me: Aesa bhi bhut war dekha gaya hai ki jis topic par post hai uske aalawa bhi bhut kuch extra add kar dete hai post me jiska koi matlab hi nahi hota.. aesa bilkul naa kare. Mistake 39:Blog me Bina faltu ke widget lagana : Ye Galti Naye Blogger karte hi hai, q ki unko nahi pata hota konsa widget lagaye ya konsa nahi, to unko jo bhi widget milte hai wo sab laga dete hai, jisse site ki speed bhi kam hoti hai or unka koi faida bhi nahi hota. Mistake 40:Blog me Email Subscribe Box add Nahi karna : EMail Subscriber Widget add karne se visitor aasani se email daal kar uspar subscribe kar sakte hai, jisse jab bhi new post publish hoti hai to uski notification email par chali jati hai.. iss trha free me traffic mil jata hai. Email Subscriber Widget kaise add kare uski jankari yaha di hui hai. Mistake 41:Blog Me social share button add na karna : Agar kisi reader ko aapki post pasand aai, ya usme jo jankari hai wo dusre se bhi share karna chata hai to uski sabuliyat ke liye share buttoin hona bhut jaruri hai. Agar aapke Blog me nahi hai to abhi add kare. Mistake 42:Blog ke Social Page Naa banana: Agar aapka Blog hai or aap usko social site par promote karna chate hai apne blog follower se to blog ka Page jarur banaye social sites par. Social Page kaise banaye uski jankari: Facebook Page Kaise Banaye Google+ Page kaise banaye Twitter Page kaise banaye Pinterest me Page Banaye Mistake 43:Blog Me social button add naa karna : Blog ke jitne bhi social page hai uspar visitor direct blog se hi follow kar sake iss liye Social Follow Widget jarur add kare. Social Follow Widget Kaise add kare uski jankari yaha hai. Mistake 44:Blog Link Exchange karna: Kuch log Backlink or traffic ke chakkar me link exchange karte hai, ki kisi dusre site ki link apni site par lagate hai or apni site ki unke site par.. par isse faida hone se jada nuksan hota hai or Google bhi isko Bad Backlink manta hai. Mistake 45:Adsense ko Time se Pahle apply kar dena : ye bhul bahut se blogger karte hai.

Agar aap Google Blogger (Blogspot) use karte hai to apko hosting ki power ke bare me dekhne ki koi jarurat nahi hai kyonki Blogger platform me apki site Google ke server par host hoti hai.Apni kosis banaye rakhe ki apki site kam se kam 4 seconds me hi open ho jaye.
For example kisi group picture me apko kewal ek apni hi picture ko main picture banani hai baki sab hatana hai.Brush & Pencil Tool (Shortcut B )Is brush tool hai, jisme brush hoti hai jise apne picture par kahi brush aur pencil se mark ka sign kar sakte hai.Paint Bucket Tool (Shortcut G )Is tool me ek hi bar me pure layer me color se full kar sakte hai, for example maan lo apka photo ka background ekdam white hai, to ese me aap is tool ka use karke use red bhi kar sakte hai.Blur Tool (Shortcut R )Jab apko photo me koi part blur karna ho yaani dhundala karna ho, kai bar hame koi part nahi dikhana hota hai ya kisi kisi aur reason se use blur karne ke liye iska use hota hai.DodgeTool (Shortcut O )Jab hame kisi photo me dark aur light karna hai tab yah tool use me lete hai.

Youtube se Paise kaise kamaye or kaise Channel ko monetize kare uske ware me phele hi bata chuka hu, agar aap new hai to [&#8230;] The post Youtube Partner Program 4,000 hour/1,000 subscriber Limit Update in Hindi appeared first on Hindi Me Help. Youtube jo ki ek aesa platform hai yaha koi bhi apne Video upload karke duniya se share kar sakta hai, or Video ko monetize karke usse paise bhi kama sakta hai. Youtube se Paise kaise kamaye or kaise Channel ko monetize kare uske ware me phele hi bata chuka hu, agar aap new hai to aap yaha dekh sakte hai. Youtube se apniYoutube Partner Program (YPP) me ek bada update kiya hai jisse jo chote channel hai wo ab paise nahi kama payege, abhi me ussi update ke ware me batane wala hu.. ki wo kya hai or uski kya limits hai. Youtube ne kuch time phele ek update kiya tha, jisme channel ke total views 10,000 hoge, uske baad hi monetize enable hoga.. lekin ab thoda usse bhi muskil hone wala hai. Youtube Partner Program Update Kya hai Youtube Channel ko monetize chalu karne ke liye Channel ke pichle 12 mahino me 4,000 hours watch time hona jaruri hai or uske sath 1,000 subscriber bhi. Ye aap Youtube Official Blog par bhi read kar sakte hai. Starting me monetize enable karne ke liye total 10,000 views to chaiye hi, par uske sath sath ab 4000 Hours/1000 subscriber bhi hona jaruri hai pichle 12 mahino me. Ye jo Update hai wo 20 February 2018 se apply ho jayega.. Agar aapki channel new hai, ya aap New Channel banane ka soch rahe hai jispar monetize enable nahi hai to aapko ye limit puri karni hogi, uske baad hi monetize on hoga.. Agar aapki channel par monetize on hai, par aapki channel par jada views nahi aate, or aapki channel par pichle ek saal me 4000 hours watch time se kam hai or 1000 subscriber se kam bade hai to aapka monetize bhi disable ho jayega. Jese hi jo limit hai wo puri hoti hai, monetize ke liye apply kar sakte hai.. Agar aapka phele monetize on tha, par new limit ke karan disable hua hai to aap badiya video dale or jese hi aapki limit puri ho.. aap suspend hone ke ek mahine baad double se apply kar sakte hai. Youtube ka khena hai, ye update unhone youtube creators ke liye hi kiya hai, taki jo galat kaam karte hai wo dur rahe. Youtube par 90% aesi channels hai jinki one year ki earning 100$ se kam hai ya ek mahine me 2$ hoti hai, aesi channel ab monetize nahi hopayegi. At Last: Mere hisab se to ye update bhut badiya hai, q ki agar aese channel hai jo 100$ se kam kamate the ek saal me.. to agar kisi ki aesi channel hai to wo ab earning ko naa dekhte huee badiya video dalege, or fir jada views aayege to earning bhi jada hogi. Aapko Kya lagta hai Youtube Partner Program ka ye update acha hai ya bura, or isse aapke youtube channel par kya aasar padha wo bhi share kare.. or agar isse sambandit koi sabal ho to aap wo bhi jarur puche. Apna Career kisme banaye, kya kare achi [&#8230;] The post Apna Interest Kisme Hai kaise Pata Kare : Career Kaise Select Kare appeared first on Hindi Me Help. Aapka Interest kisme hai or kis chij me apna career banaye jo aap usme success bhi ho sake or apni success ko injoy bhi kar sake.. Aapko sahi khusi jab hogi jab aap wo kare jisko karne me aapko maja aata hai or aap usme success ho jaye. Apna Career kisme banaye, kya kare achi jindgi jine ke liye jisme sab kuch ho jo aap chate hai ye jaanna to sab chate hoge, or ye mod har ek ki life me ek war aata hai jab unko ye fesla lena padta haiki ab aage unko kya karna hai or kaise apni life ko jina hai. Me Aapko is article me ye hi batane wala hu ki aap kaise apne Interest, Passion or Talent ko phechane or usme aapko career banana hai ya nahi ye kaisedecide kare.. uski kuch tips duga.. jiske baad aap apni life ko kese jina hai thoda or achi se samaj paoge. Jab muje mera passion jaanna tha to mene apne aap se kuch sabal puche theor jab muje unka jabab mile to me samaj gaya muje apni life me kya karna hai. Aapka apna passion kis chij me hai ye jaanne ke liye aapko bhi wo sabal apne aap se puchna hoge, jo mene apne aap se puche the.. Agar aapne abhi tak Meri Success Story nahi padhi to aapko jarur padhna chaiye.

(u'www.hindimehelp.com', u'/zebpay-me-paise-add-kaise-kare/', u'Zebpay Me Paise Add Kaise Kare Bitcoin Kharidne ke liye | Hindi Me HelpHomeBloggingBloggerWordPressBloggingSEOGuest PostsSocial MediaFacebookTwitterYouTubeGoogleWhatsappSocial NetworkInternetImportant WebsiteToolsInternetMake MoneyMotivationalMoreComputerMobileFestivalHMHSearchHindi Me HelpHomeBloggingBloggerWordPressBloggingSEOGuest PostsSocial MediaFacebookTwitterYouTubeGoogleWhatsappSocial NetworkInternetImportant WebsiteToolsInternetMake MoneyMotivationalMoreComputerMobileFestivalHMHHomeMake MoneyZebpay Me Paise Add Kaise Kare Bitcoin Kharidne ke liyeMake MoneyZebpay Me Paise Add Kaise Kare Bitcoin Kharidne ke liyeBy Rohit Mewada - December 13, 201732Facebook Twitter Google+ WhatsApp PinterestAgar aapne Bitcoin ke ware me suna hai or aap chate hai me bhi kuch paise ka investment Bitcoin me karu to aap badi aasani se kar sakte hai.Me phele hi bata chuka hu India me Bitcoin kaise kharide, agar aapne wo post read nahi ki hai to phele usko read kare.. iske sath sath jo Trusted or Popular Bitcoin ki website or Apphai unki list yaha hai, aap insab par apna account bana kar rakhe.Bitcoin kharidne ke bhut tarike hai, jisme se India me jo popular hai wo hai Zebpay or Unocoin, jinse ham badi aasani se Bank se paise transfer karke Bitcoin kharid sakte hai.Zebpay se Bitcoin Kaise KharideZebpay se Bitcoin kharidne ke liye to sabse phele aapko uska App install karna hoga, to agar aapne abhi tak nahi kiya hai to abhi kar lijiye, Install karne ke baad aapko apna account verify karana hoga.. Zebpay Account kaise Verify karna hai uski jankari aapko yaha mil jayegi..Download ZebpayAb agar aapne App Install karke usme account bana liya hai, or apne Document upload karke apna account bhi verify kar liya hai to aap Zebpay se Bitcoin kharidne ke liye teyar hai.Zebpay se Bitcoin kharidne ke liye kya kya chaiyeFully Verify Zebpay AccountAapka Bank Account Bank Account me Net Banking chalu hona bhut jaruri hai, ussi se paise add hoge.Bank Account me Paise Zebpay se Bitcoin kharidne ke liye phele aapko Zebpay me Paise add karna padege, fir aap unn paiso se Bitcoin kharid sakte hai..Zebpay me Paise Add (deposit) Kaise kareZebpay me Paise add karna bhut aasan hai, wass iske liye aapko apni uss bank account me net banking chalu hona jaruri hai, jo aapne Zebpay Account me Verify me dali hai.Step 1: Sabse phele App me Deposit ki button par click kare.Step 2: Ab Paise add karne ke liye option aayege.Paise Add karne ke liye 3 option aayege, jisme me personally Express Transfer ko use karta hu.Express Transfer me aapko ek Zebpay ka account diya jayega jo aapko Bank account me beneficiary add karna hoga, uske baad aap aasani se paise uss account me transfer kar sakte hai, iski limit 21 15,00,000 tak ek din me kar sakte hai, (isme Net Banking ka koi charge nahi lagega)Payment Gateway PayU me direct NetBanking se login karke transfer kar sakte hai.
Aise hi likhte rahiye.

taki kisi bhi version me agar koi problem ho to uska pata aapko chal sake.Note: agar aap apni site par HTTPs use karte hai jab hi aapko https ke sath add karne ki jarurat hai.Blogspot domain me HTTPS kaise enable kare uski jankari yaha hai.#2: Site ko www ya non-www select kare.Aap apni site ka jo url hai wo www ke sath ya bina www ke use karte hai wo select kare, taki google site ko ussi format me dikhaye search me.iske liye aapko search console me setting me jakar select karna hai.Aap site ko jisme open karna chate hai wo select kar lijiye, uske baad save kar dijiye.. jese aap dekh sakte hai HindiMeHelp.com ko mene without www select kiya hai.. isse jada kuch fark nahi padta aap kuch bhi select kar sakte hai.. wass iss baat ka dhiyan rakhe jese aapki website open hoti hai aap wahi select kare.Agar aapka Blog Blogspot par hai to without www kaise open kare uski jankari yaha hai.#3: Target Country select kare site ke liyeAapki jo website hai, uska main target konsi country hai aap wo select kare, taki jo data aapko dikhaya jaye Search Console me wo ussi ke hisab se ho.Target country add karne ke liye aapko Search Traffic >>International Targeting >> Country par jana hai, fir apni jo bhi target country hai wo select karke save karna hai.Note: Agar aap Country Specific Domain extension use karte hai, jese .in, .pk, .us to usme automatic country aa jayegi or aapko yaha country select karne ka option nahi aayega.#4: SiteMap Submit kare Search Console meWebsite ka Sitemap Submit karna bhi bhut jaruri hai, q ki issi ki madad se search engine ko pata karne me aasani hoti hai ki hamari site par kitni post hai, kitne page hai.

chalna padta hai, to uska fast hona bhi bhut jaruri hai.Agar aapka computer Slow hai to Computer ki speed kaise badaye uski jankari yaha hai.Mistake 56:Slow Internet ( 2G ) par work karna : Slow Internet use karna bhi galat hai, q ki agar aap slow Internet use karege to 1 second ki chij 3 second me load hogi, to isse aap hi andaja laga lijiye kitna jada time barbad hoga.Mistake 57:Blog Ki Har jankari de, taki war war aapke visitor inko read karke apna time kharab naa kare.Mistake 58:Post Me jyada images add karna : Upar ek Point me bataya tha ki kam se kam ek Image to use jarur kare, par iss baat ka bhi dhiyan rakhe ki bhut jada image bhi use naa kare, nahi to loading time bad jayega Isliye sirf kaam ki Image hi use kare.Upload karne se Phele Image ko Compress karke Size kam kareMistake 59:Professional Logo Na Lagana : Blog ka ek badiya Logo hona bhi jaruri hai taki koi bhi usko dekhe to unko yaad rahe, jo Branding ke liye bhi bhut jaruri hai.Agar ek badiya logo hoga to website me char chand to usse hi lag jayege.Aap Online Free Tool se Logo bana sakte hai.Mistake 60:War War Design change karna : Blog ka badiya design hona bhut jaruri hai, par ussi ke sath ye bhi hai ki agar war war design change kare to uska SEO me bhi bura aasar padta hai.. to iss baat ka dhiyan rakhe or first time me hi ek badiya design select kare..Mistake 61:Spelling me Mistake karna : blog padhne vale visitor aapki writing skill aur spelling ko dekhkar hi pehchan lete hai ki aap kaise blogger ho.

Aapki WhatsApp Profile Pic Kisne Dekhi Kaise Jane Facebook Or WhatsApp Par Chat Karnewale Ki Location Kaise Pata Kare Blacklist Se Number Kaise Nikale Aur Block Number Ko Unblock Kaise Kare Apne Number Ki Call Details Kaise Nikale Apne number ki call history jane ke liye 3 tarike hai.1st ki aapka jo bhi sim hai usko aap online manage kar call history dekh sakte hai.It mean agar aap idea sim hai toh aap idea ki official site idea cellular par ja kar apna online account bana lijiye.Vaha par aapke number se realated most of information aapko mil jayegi.But is tarike me kuch sim ki perfect details nahi milti hai.2nd Apne mobile me Trucaller app ko pehle se hi installed rakhe.Is app me aap deleted number and records ki bhi call history dekh sakte hai.Or Mobile number ka naam,location bhi trace kar sakte hai.3rd tarika sab se best tarika hai jise mai puri detail me niche share kar raha hoon.

Hello Friends, aaj ka Topic thoda interesting hai.. q ki aaj ham Blogging or hamari Life ko connect karege, or janege ki kya faide hai ek blogger se shaadi karne par. Agar aap ek blogger hai to aapko pata hona chaiye Blogging karne ke kya kya faide hai, or agar aap Blogger nahi hai par aap kisi Blogger se shaadi karne ka soch rahe hai to aapko kya kya faide hoge, un sabhi point ke upar ham baat karge. Sabse phele thoda jaan lete hai Blogger hota kon hai ? Blogger Kon Hota Hai ? Blogger wo person hota hai, jiska koi Blog(Website) hota hai jispar wo khud se likh kar Post dalta hai.. Un post ke jariye wo apne Talent or Passion ko duniya se share karta hai, or usse Earning bhi karta hai. Blog Kaise banaye uski jankari aapko yaha mil jayegi, agar aap abhi tak ek Blogger nahi hai ..

To aap bilkul sahi post par aaye hai, isme me aapko batane wala hu, SEO kya hai, kaise SEO karte hai or kitne type ke SEO hote hai jo hamari site ko search engine (google) me lane me madad karte hai. Agar aapne abhi abhi blogging start ki hai or aap iss baat se paresan hai ki aapki site search karne par top par q nahi aati, to iska sidha sa matlab hai aapko SEO kya hai or wo kitna jaruri hai ye aapko pata nahi hai. SEO Kya Hai ? Seo Kya hai: SEO ka meaning Hota hai (Search Engine Optimize). Simple sabdo me kahe to, Search Engine Optimize ka matlab hai hamari site ko iss trha se teyar karna ki usme kya hai wo search engine (Google, Yahoo, Bing) achi se samaj sake or search me dikhaye. Ye to aap jante hi hoge ki ham kuch bhi google me search karte hai to google hame kisi site ki link de deta hai, SEO me ham Google ko hi batate hai ki hamari site me ye hai.
